<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When an object is instantiated, if a static method exists that is injectable, it gets called by Zend\Di.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
class One {}
class Two {
    public static $one = false;
    public static function setSomethingStatically(One $one)
    {
        static::$one = $one;
    }
}
$di = new \Zend\Di\Di();


$di-&gt;instanceManager()
   -&gt;addTypePreference('One', new One());

$two = $di-&gt;get('Two');

$two::$one !== false;
</code></pre>

